  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e1fa6e7475b5db645b383f0b31df8a81, type: 3}
  m_Name: DialogLv5
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - characterName: "Th\u1EE3 l\u1EB7n"
    content: Those ruins were grim. I feel like I just escaped an ancient tomb.
    characterIcon: {fileID: 0}
    isRightSide: 0
  - characterName: "Ti\u1EBFn s\u0129"
    content: "That was only the beginning. Our final destination is 'The Titan' \u2014
      the deepest abyss. The pressure down there could crush our ship like a tin
      can."
    characterIcon: {fileID: 0}
    isRightSide: 1
  - characterName: "Th\u1EE3 l\u1EB7n"
    content: Rudders, compasses, treasure chests... is that all that's left of hope?
    characterIcon: {fileID: 0}
    isRightSide: 0
  - characterName: "Ti\u1EBFn s\u0129"
    content: The end of the journey lies there. This is our final leap. Bring them
      back, and we will rewrite history.
    characterIcon: {fileID: 0}
    isRightSide: 1
